| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0583 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 212c3dbe-0047-5ca7-ab10-f1a81cbc44fc"
